textBox.richText: Started over at the Zephyr; worked our way over to Jane fairly quickly. No Cheshire Cat, but Sidetrack and Sleeper were open. One run down there, and Alli’s calves weren’t happy with her, so Gunter, Max, and I did a couple laps. After lunch, they opened up Gandy again...MUCH softer and less nasties than it looked from the bottom. Max was done after a little, so Mom came and got him, and Gunter and I played around some more....hit more bumps, a little trees, and some jumps.
